<section class="section work__highlight highlight--dual highlight--para">
  <article>
    <img src="/assets/img/circle--yellow--dashed.svg" alt="" />
    

    <h3>
      Direction
    </h3>
    <p>
      Varun agreed with the general aesthetic I was looking to go with, but he still couldnâ€™t see that intuitive message that this was a filmmakerâ€™s website. During one of our conversations, we came up with the idea of playing a short looping video in the backgroundâ€”that would have something to do with filmmaking, or films in general.
    </p>
  </article>
  <article>

    <h3>
      Plan Forward
    </h3>
    <p>
      Thanks to the fact that Varun had access to all the equipment we might need to shoot the video, I had the opportunity to art-direct my own shoot. The general direction of the video was to shoot equipment or scenarios that indicated something "meta-film".
    </p>
  </article>
</section>

